# Logos

## Design & Color

The logos of the applications or sites that use the Puzzle Shell should have a consistent look. This concept defines the parts and colors such a logo incorporates:

- A Puzzle Shell logo consists of a first part, that is a portion of the offical Puzzle ITC logo (without the "ITC") and a second part with the name of the given application or site (ideally one word).

- The font used for the application name is _Roboto_, with size _16px_ and weight _700_.

- There are two different colors that can be used for the application name, depending on the character of the application:
